   196→  /// [repositoryProvider.getResources]: Returns session's ResourceData which doesn't include BallInfo.positions and BallInfo.ball.presignedAnnotatedVideoUrl and BallInfo.ball.presignedExtractedVideoUrl
   197→  /// [repositoryProvider.getResourceDetail]: Returns a specific ResourceDAta which include BallInfo.positions but doesn't include BallInfo.ball.presignedAnnotatedVideoUrl and BallInfo.ball.presignedExtractedVideoUrl
